{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775897561816,"sessionID":"ses_28444448bffe4NK7jHwHVmw2ww","part":{"id":"prt_d7bbca83e001hxYtlqwwHCUEmn","messageID":"msg_d7bbc8b24001NKOuY1mHP3Yw9w","sessionID":"ses_28444448bffe4NK7jHwHVmw2ww","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:14","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/cmd/cli/tasks.md","content":"# AR-025 — MetadataService and Data Models\n\n> **Module:** `cmd/cli`\n> **Language:** Python\n> **Size:** M\n> **Stage:** ST-3 (Design) Completed → ST-4 (Implementation)\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.1 — AgentMetadata Model Enhancement\n\n### Tasks\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.1.1 | Add `model_config` to `AgentMetadata` with `populate_by_name=True`, `validate_assignment=True`, `extra='forbid'` | Unit test: extra fields raise ValidationError | 0.5h |\n| 4.1.2 | Add field `pack_timestamp: Optional[str]` with description \"ISO timestamp of pack operation\" | Unit test: field serializes/deserializes correctly | 0.5h |\n| 4.1.3 | Add field `dockerfile_generated: Optional[bool]` with description \"Whether Dockerfile was generated\" | Unit test: field serializes/deserializes correctly | 0.5h |\n| 4.1.4 | Verify `language` validator accepts lowercase/uppercase, rejects invalid values | Unit test: \"Python\"→\"python\", \"invalid\" raises ValueError | 0.5h |\n| 4.1.5 | Verify `build_mode` validator accepts lowercase/uppercase, rejects invalid values | Unit test: \"Local\"→\"local\", \"invalid\" raises ValueError | 0.5h |\n| 4.1.6 | Verify `port` validator rejects ports outside 1-65535 | Unit test: 0 raises ValueError, 65536 raises ValueError, 8080 passes | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** AgentMetadata model fully configured with validation.\n\n**Files:**\n- `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` - AgentMetadata class\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.2 — MetadataOptions Dataclass\n\n### Tasks\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.2.1 | Implement `MetadataOptions` dataclass with all fields per design spec | `dataclasses.fields(MetadataOptions)` returns expected fields | 0.5h |\n| 4.2.2 | Implement `MetadataOptions.from_options()` class method filtering unknown keys | Unit test: unknown keys ignored, known keys preserved | 0.5h |\n| 4.2.3 | Verify all fields have correct default values | Unit test: `MetadataOptions()` has expected defaults | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** MetadataOptions dataclass for CLI option handling.\n\n**Files:**\n- `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` - MetadataOptions class\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.3 — MetadataService Core Operations\n\n### Tasks\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.3.1 | Implement `METADATA_FILENAMES` class constant with precedence order | Unit test: constant equals ['agent_metadata.yaml', 'agent.yaml', 'metadata.yaml'] | 0.5h |\n| 4.3.2 | Implement `__init__()` with verbose logging setup | Unit test: verbose=True sets DEBUG level | 0.5h |\n| 4.3.3 | Implement `load_metadata()` with filename fallback chain | Unit test: finds agent_metadata.yaml before agent.yaml before metadata.yaml | 1h |\n| 4.3.4 | Handle missing metadata file by creating default in `load_metadata()` | Unit test: missing file calls `_create_default_metadata()` | 1h |\n| 4.3.5 | Implement `save_metadata()` writing to agent_metadata.yaml with correct YAML formatting | Unit test: file created, default_flow_style=False, indent=2, sort_keys=False | 1h |\n| 4.3.6 | Implement `save_metadata()` with `exclude_none=True` to omit null values | Unit test: None values not written to YAML | 0.5h |\n| 4.3.7 | Implement `update_metadata()` for load-update-save cycle | Unit test: updates applied and persisted to file | 1h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Core CRUD operations for metadata persistence.\n\n**Files:**\n- `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` - MetadataService class\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.4 — MetadataService Workspace Validation\n\n### Tasks\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.4.1 | Implement `validate_workspace()` checking workspace exists and is directory | Unit test: non-existent path raises ValueError, file path raises ValueError | 0.5h |\n| 4.4.2 | Implement `validate_workspace()` dispatching to language-specific validators | Unit test: python calls _validate_python_workspace, java calls _validate_java_workspace | 0.5h |\n| 4.4.3 | Implement `_validate_python_workspace()` requiring at least one *.py file | Unit test: workspace with .py passes, without raises ValueError | 0.5h |\n| 4.4.4 | Implement `_validate_java_workspace()` requiring pom.xml | Unit test: workspace with pom.xml passes, without raises ValueError | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Workspace validation for Python and Java agents.\n\n**Files:**\n- `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` - validation methods\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.5 — MetadataService Default Metadata Creation\n\n### Tasks\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.5.1 | Implement `_create_default_metadata()` inferring agent_name from directory name | Unit test: /path/to/my-agent → agent_name=\"my-agent\" | 0.5h |\n| 4.5.2 | Implement `_infer_entrypoint()` for Python workspaces | Unit test: finds main.py, app.py, server.py in priority order | 1h |\n| 4.5.3 | Implement `_infer_entrypoint()` defaulting to \"python main.py\" when no candidate found | Unit test: returns \"python main.py\" when no files exist | 0.5h |\n| 4.5.4 | Implement `_infer_entrypoint()` for Java workspaces returning \"java -jar app.jar\" | Unit test: returns \"java -jar app.jar\" for Java language | 0.5h |\n| 4.5.5 | Ensure `_create_default_metadata()` creates valid AgentMetadata with required fields | Unit test: created metadata passes AgentMetadata.model_validate() | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Automatic metadata inference from workspace contents.\n\n**Files:**\n- `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` - helper methods\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.6 — Unit Tests — AgentMetadata Model\n\n### Tasks\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.6.1 | Write test `test_valid_metadata_creation` — create with all required fields | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.6.2 | Write test `test_language_validation_valid` — python, Python, JAVA | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.6.3 | Write test `test_language_validation_invalid` — invalid raises ValueError | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.6.4 | Write test `test_build_mode_validation_valid` — local, cloud, Local, Cloud | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.6.5 | Write test `test_build_mode_validation_invalid` — invalid raises ValueError | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.6.6 | Write test `test_port_validation_valid` — 1, 8080, 65535 | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.6.7 | Write test `test_port_validation_invalid` — 0, 65536, -1 raise ValueError | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.6.8 | Write test `test_serialization_roundtrip` — to dict and back | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.6.9 | Write test `test_extra_fields_forbidden` — extra field raises ValidationError | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.6.10 | Write test `test_optional_fields_none` — optional fields can be None | Pass | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Comprehensive unit tests for AgentMetadata.\n\n**Files:**\n- `tests/test_metadata_model.py` - AgentMetadata tests\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.7 — Unit Tests — MetadataOptions\n\n### Tasks\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.7.1 | Write test `test_defaults` — verify default field values | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.7.2 | Write test `test_from_options` — create from dict with valid keys | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.7.3 | Write test `test_from_options_ignores_unknown` — unknown keys filtered out | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.7.4 | Write test `test_from_options_filters_none` — None values filtered | Pass | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Unit tests for MetadataOptions.\n\n**Files:**\n- `tests/test_pack_models.py` - MetadataOptions tests\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.8 — Unit Tests — MetadataService Load/Save\n\n### Tasks\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.8.1 | Write test `test_load_existing_metadata` — load from agent_metadata.yaml | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.8.2 | Write test `test_load_with_fallback_agent_yaml` — falls back to agent.yaml | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.8.3 | Write test `test_load_with_fallback_metadata_yaml` — falls back to metadata.yaml | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.8.4 | Write test `test_load_creates_default` — creates default when no file exists | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.8.5 | Write test `test_load_invalid_yaml_raises_error` — malformed YAML raises ValueError | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.8.6 | Write test `test_save_metadata_creates_file` — file created at correct path | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.8.7 | Write test `test_save_metadata_excludes_none` — None values not in output | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.8.8 | Write test `test_save_metadata_formatting` — correct YAML formatting | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.8.9 | Write test `test_update_metadata` — updates applied and saved | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.8.10 | Write test `test_update_metadata_unknown_field_warns` — unknown field logs warning | Pass | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Comprehensive tests for load/save/update operations.\n\n**Files:**\n- `tests/test_metadata_service.py` - MetadataService tests\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.9 — Unit Tests — MetadataService Validation\n\n### Tasks\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.9.1 | Write test `test_validate_workspace_not_exists` — raises ValueError | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.9.2 | Write test `test_validate_workspace_not_directory` — raises ValueError | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.9.3 | Write test `test_validate_python_workspace_success` — with .py files passes | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.9.4 | Write test `test_validate_python_workspace_no_files` — no .py raises ValueError | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.9.5 | Write test `test_validate_java_workspace_success` — with pom.xml passes | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.9.6 | Write test `test_validate_java_workspace_no_pom` — no pom.xml raises ValueError | Pass | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Tests for workspace validation.\n\n**Files:**\n- `tests/test_metadata_service.py` - validation tests\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.10 — Unit Tests — Default Metadata Creation\n\n### Tasks\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.10.1 | Write test `test_create_default_metadata_agent_name` — inferred from path | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.10.2 | Write test `test_infer_entrypoint_python_main` — finds main.py | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.10.3 | Write test `test_infer_entrypoint_python_app` — finds app.py | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.10.4 | Write test `test_infer_entrypoint_python_server` — finds server.py | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.10.5 | Write test `test_infer_entrypoint_python_default` — defaults to main.py | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.10.6 | Write test `test_infer_entrypoint_java` — returns jar command | Pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.10.7 | Write test `test_default_metadata_valid` — passes model validation | Pass | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Tests for default metadata inference.\n\n**Files:**\n- `tests/test_metadata_service.py` - default metadata tests\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.11 — Integration Tests\n\n### Tasks\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.11.1 | Write test `test_metadata_roundtrip` — save then load preserves all fields | Pass | 1h |\n| 4.11.2 | Write test `test_metadata_yaml_format` — verify output matches design spec format | Pass | 1h |\n| 4.11.3 | Write test `test_python_workspace_pack_flow` — full flow with Python files | Pass | 1h |\n| 4.11.4 | Write test `test_java_workspace_pack_flow` — full flow with pom.xml | Pass | 1h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Integration tests for end-to-end workflows.\n\n**Files:**\n- `tests/test_metadata_integration.py` - integration tests\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.12 — Documentation & Package Exports\n\n### Tasks\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.12.1 | Update `agentcube/services/__init__.py` to export MetadataService and AgentMetadata | `from agentcube.services import MetadataService, AgentMetadata` works | 0.5h |\n| 4.12.2 | Update `agentcube/models/__init__.py` to export MetadataOptions | `from agentcube.models import MetadataOptions` works | 0.5h |\n| 4.12.3 | Verify all public classes have docstrings | `pydoc agentcube.services.MetadataService` shows docstring | 0.5h |\n| 4.12.4 | Verify module docstrings present | File headers describe module purpose | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Proper exports and documentation.\n\n**Files:**\n- `agentcube/services/__init__.py`\n- `agentcube/models/__init__.py`\n- `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n- `agentcube/models/pack_models.py`\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.13 — Final Verification\n\n### Tasks\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.13.1 | Run all unit tests: `pytest tests/test_metadata_*.py -v` | 100% pass rate | 0.5h |\n| 4.13.2 | Verify test coverage: `pytest --cov=agentcube.services --cov=agentcube.models` | >80% coverage | 0.5h |\n| 4.13.3 | Verify type checking: `mypy agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | No errors | 0.5h |\n| 4.13.4 | Verify linting: `ruff check agentcube/services/ agentcube/models/` | No errors | 0.5h |\n| 4.13.5 | Verify imports work: `python -c \"from agentcube.services import MetadataService; from agentcube.models import MetadataOptions\"` | No ImportError | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** All verification checks pass.\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n| Phase | Tasks | Est. Hours |\n|-------|-------|------------|\n| ST-4.1: AgentMetadata Model | 6 | 3h |\n| ST-4.2: MetadataOptions | 3 | 1.5h |\n| ST-4.3: Core Operations | 7 | 5h |\n| ST-4.4: Workspace Validation | 4 | 2h |\n| ST-4.5: Default Metadata | 5 | 3h |\n| ST-4.6: Unit Tests (Model) | 10 | 5h |\n| ST-4.7: Unit Tests (Options) | 4 | 2h |\n| ST-4.8: Unit Tests (Service) | 10 | 5h |\n| ST-4.9: Unit Tests (Validation) | 6 | 3h |\n| ST-4.10: Unit Tests (Defaults) | 7 | 3.5h |\n| ST-4.11: Integration Tests | 4 | 4h |\n| ST-4.12: Documentation | 4 | 2h |\n| ST-4.13: Verification | 5 | 2.5h |\n| **Total** | **75** | **41.5h** |\n\n---\n\n## File Deliverables Checklist\n\n### Source Files\n- [ ] `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` — MetadataService + AgentMetadata\n- [ ] `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` — MetadataOptions\n\n### Test Files\n- [ ] `tests/test_metadata_model.py` — AgentMetadata model tests\n- [ ] `tests/test_pack_models.py` — MetadataOptions tests\n- [ ] `tests/test_metadata_service.py` — MetadataService tests\n- [ ] `tests/test_metadata_integration.py` — Integration tests\n\n### Package Files\n- [ ] `agentcube/services/__init__.py` — Service exports\n- [ ] `agentcube/models/__init__.py` — Model exports\n\n---\n\n## Definition of Done\n\n- [ ] All 75 tasks complete\n- [ ] All unit tests pass (>80% coverage)\n- [ ] All integration tests pass\n- [ ] Type checker (mypy) clean\n- [ ] Linter (ruff) clean\n- [ ] Imports work correctly\n- [ ] AgentMetadata validates all fields\n- [ ] MetadataService loads/saves/updates YAML correctly\n- [ ] Workspace validation works for Python and Java\n- [ ] Default metadata creation infers from workspace\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/agentcube/cli/__init__.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/agentcube/cli/main.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/agentcube/models/pack_models.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/cmd/cli/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/cmd/cli/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775897561803,"end":1775897561813}}